{"tid":2510952,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"居屋 2020 (10)","createTime":"2021-04-30T13:40:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T17:25:17.000Z","uid":22337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1ab9b5045e3286d931648b04e08cba52a0b0b709","tid":2510952,"uid":22337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:40:03.000Z","msg":"上個post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2402320/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2402320/</a><br />\n<br />\n『居屋2020』<a href=\"http://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/hos/2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Fhos%2F2020&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT0kSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=ebfb955d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/hos/2020</a><br />\n<br />\n『白居二2020』<a href=\"http://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/wsm/2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.housingauthority.gov.hk%2Fwsm%2F2020&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT0kSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=49f801d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.housingauthority.gov.hk/wsm/2020</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">自己睇申請須知</span></span>啦屌你老尾<br />\n有正體/殘體/英文，都睇唔掂嘅可以驗下智商<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmS1Nem5ibfo6V3hWnpHsRpyw4j35KhDQeyszGrRBsmgNp?filename=zCZw6mJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzCZw6mJ.jpg&h=1c689fd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb4f7MAPivcQGhi28ML4BXALNoW9t1Cx7eFHCvhUp47oc?filename=XGdmJ8t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXGdmJ8t.jpg&h=056d1001&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖係2019年居屋<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYywi4eLQ8F31Xm7LAChbDjvZNooxD5cEEWrQYDq5nRj6?filename=14koXtB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14koXtB.png&h=2fe2a5b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年2020年<br />\n假設受歡迎程度係 3房&gt;2房&gt;1房&gt;開放式<br />\n2100個核心長者 已經食晒 3房&amp;2房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"green\">綠表</span>及白表申請者的配額比率為 <span class=\"green\">40</span>:60<br />\n在選樓期間，每五名 出席選樓申請者的選樓次序依次為<br />\n(i)一位<span class=\"green\">綠表</span>申請者<br />\n(ii)一位白表申請者<br />\n(iii) 一位<span class=\"green\">綠表</span>申請者<br />\n(iv)一位白表申請者 以及<br />\n(v) 一位白表申請者<br />\n<br />\n「家有長者優先選樓計劃」有 2,100 個單位的配額<br />\n白表「非核心家庭申請者」將獲安排於所有白表「其他核心家庭申請者」選樓之後才選樓。<br />\n一人申請者700 個單位。<br />\n一人申請者會在家庭申請者選樓後，選購餘下任何面積的一個單位。<br />\n<br />\n問:<br />\n請教下係咪CM12揀完到GE先再到WE 然後GM再落WM<br />\n答:<br />\n綠白綠白白 &gt; 綠白綠白白 &gt; LOOP<br />\nGE1 &gt; WE1 &gt; GE2 &gt; WE2 &gt; WE3"},{"pid":"decf5c271ac013ccf31620e53450d9f689e1c4ed","tid":2510952,"uid":22337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:40:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYKdPJ3umAoQMvCdeXa2fQJpBTk5mcNTfsN4jFcyndPga?filename=FoNOeT0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFoNOeT0.png&h=b9840a1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRmHUbaerYBKxho6wwuopEzRoxrNxYj4nBJqkeYF311Tq?filename=kVb0NT8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkVb0NT8.png&h=574f3684&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5d9b8b6ca2d5540456fd9c56ce0e8f27ecc22be","tid":2510952,"uid":191224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T06:09:47.000Z","msg":"幾時出有價單呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218661a06796483c703aae8f6cf330cb73118db3","tid":2510952,"uid":71213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5d9b8b6ca2d5540456fd9c56ce